name: Classic Oatmeal Bowl
description: Steel-cut oats with fresh berries and almond butter
instructions: Cook steel-cut oats according to package directions. Top with mixed berries and a tablespoon of almond butter.

name: Protein Pancakes
description: High-protein pancakes with banana and maple syrup
instructions: Mix protein powder with eggs and banana. Cook on griddle until golden. Top with maple syrup.

name: Veggie Scramble
description: Scrambled eggs with spinach and mushrooms
instructions: Scramble eggs with fresh spinach and saut√©ed mushrooms. Season with salt and pepper.

name: Greek Yogurt Parfait
description: Greek yogurt layered with granola and berries
instructions: Layer Greek yogurt with granola and mixed berries. Drizzle with honey.

name: Breakfast Burrito
description: Whole wheat tortilla filled with eggs and black beans
instructions: Scramble eggs and warm black beans. Wrap in whole wheat tortilla with salsa.

name: Grilled Chicken Salad
description: Mixed greens with grilled chicken breast and vinaigrette
instructions: Grill chicken breast and slice. Serve over mixed greens with balsamic vinaigrette.

name: Turkey Wrap
description: Whole wheat wrap with turkey and avocado
instructions: Layer turkey slices with avocado and greens in whole wheat wrap.

name: Quinoa Buddha Bowl
description: Quinoa with roasted vegetables and tahini
instructions: Cook quinoa and roast mixed vegetables. Top with tahini dressing.

name: Tuna Salad Bowl
description: Tuna with mixed greens and olive oil
instructions: Mix canned tuna with olive oil and lemon. Serve over mixed greens.

name: Chicken Rice Bowl
description: Brown rice with grilled chicken and broccoli
instructions: Cook brown rice and steam broccoli. Top with grilled chicken.

name: Salmon & Sweet Potato
description: Baked salmon with roasted sweet potato and asparagus
instructions: Bake salmon and roast sweet potato wedges. Steam asparagus.

name: Lean Beef Stir Fry
description: Lean beef with mixed vegetables over rice
instructions: Stir fry lean beef with mixed vegetables. Serve over brown rice.

name: Turkey Meatballs & Pasta
description: Whole wheat pasta with turkey meatballs and marinara
instructions: Make turkey meatballs and bake. Cook pasta and heat marinara sauce.

name: Chicken Fajita Bowl
description: Grilled chicken with peppers and onions over cauliflower rice
instructions: Grill chicken with peppers and onions. Serve over cauliflower rice.

name: Baked Cod & Veggies
description: Baked cod with roasted Brussels sprouts and quinoa
instructions: Bake cod filet and roast Brussels sprouts. Serve with cooked quinoa.

name: Protein Shake
description: Whey protein with banana and almond milk
instructions: Blend protein powder with banana and almond milk.

name: Apple & Almond Butter
description: Sliced apple with almond butter
instructions: Slice apple and serve with 2 tablespoons almond butter.

name: Cottage Cheese & Berries
description: Low-fat cottage cheese with mixed berries
instructions: Top cottage cheese with fresh mixed berries.

name: Hard Boiled Eggs
description: Two hard-boiled eggs with sea salt
instructions: Boil eggs for 10 minutes. Peel and season with sea salt.

name: Greek Yogurt & Nuts
description: Greek yogurt with mixed nuts
instructions: Top Greek yogurt with a handful of mixed nuts.
